Package: dcom99.bag9031
Title: An OpenWeatherMap.org Data Retrieval/Visualization Tool
Version: 1.0.0
Imports: ZipRadius, dplyr, jsonlite, magrittr, ggplot2, methods,
        lubridate, rtweet, scales, tibble, stats, leaflet, gridExtra,
        tidyr, shiny, stringr
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Douglas",
           family = "Comstock",
